token_info.name: Joker 1 - Deck of Demise
token_info.description: Joker #1 (of 2) in the "Deck of Demise" series. These NFTs will be given to all addresses which hold an entire deck of "Deck of Demise" NFTs and will not be sold. This NFT appears as an unedited, uninscribed, playing card, though there is a hidden inscription. See OBJKT 36050 for series details.
